      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOO BUSY (4) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (17.30). Can atone. SPEEDY ED (2) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. In the money last time at this track (17.19) in a Grade 5/6, finishing a 1.75 lengths second. Looks suited here and can measure up. QUEST FOR STEPS (7) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (17.27) at this track. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from three starts. Will give a great sight again. BETTER HALF (8) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
